check the date from shp if it doesn't match update the quote.
get the date from the shared pref to update the next day quote.

change text size of quote
change text size of author

change font size of quote
change font size of author

alignment change of author (only)

check cardview size and set author text according to it. Take quote for reference.
Please note once you saved the settings it will change in the next widget update.
Please note once you saved the settings it will change when the next time widget updates.
Please note your saved settings will come into effect in the next widget updates.

